description: The follow up album to New Orleans, LA native Mystikal's near-gold debut, Mind of Mystikal (which contained several rap hits including "Y'All Ain't Ready Yet," "Here I Go" and "Out That Boot Camp Clicc") pairs the distinctive rap artist with red-hot artist/producer Master P. Master P has the "Midas touch" with 2 gold albums to his credit and has worked with platinum rappers E-40, Big Mike and Foxy Brown. 1st single, serviced to rap, R&B and rhythm crossover radio and mix shows and clubs, is the title track.
title: Unpredictable explicit_lyrics
